{"tid":1982864,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"突破人眼極限！三星宣布研發6億畫素感光元件","createTime":"2020-04-21T12:29:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T19:48:57.000Z","uid":32511,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2578d87633e62d8325dc2b1b0a30f3afa2ae50c8","tid":1982864,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:29:16.000Z","msg":"週二 (21 日) 三星 LSI 執行副總 Yongin Park 在官網發文表示，目前三星準備研製 6 億像素 (600MP) 感光元件，已直接突破人眼極限 (約 5 億像素)，與 SONY 的模組競爭如火如荼的進行中。<br />\n<br />\n自去年三星推出了 6400 萬像素的 ISOCELL GWX 感光元件後，隨後亦推出為小米設計的 ISOCELL HM1 / HMX 感光元件，其也安裝至最新的 Galaxy S20 機型，能搭載 1 億 800 萬像素相機，此前更有消息稱三星正在研發 1 億 500 萬像素 Nonacell 圖像感光元件，週二 (21 日) 更直接宣布將展開研發 600MP 感光元件。<br />\n<br />\n而 600MP 感光元件研發計畫中，預計將能超過人眼可以看出的大約 500MP 的解析度，相比之下，多數市場上單眼相機和手機分別提供 40MP 和 12MP 感光元件，在與人眼解析度相比之前，看似還有很長的路要走。<br />\n<br />\n技術方面 600MP 預計將類似於當前 108MP 感光元件的九合一技術，將藉助多像素合成技術來模擬大底，改善相片質量等，不過可能需要新的材料等技術引入。<br />\n除了 600MP 的研發外，Yongin Park 還提到也正著手研發可捕捉人眼之外 (450nm 至 750nm 以上) 光波的感光元件，比如紫外線傳感器可用於檢測皮膚癌，紅外線感光元件用於工業質量控制等。<br />\n<br />\n有報導指出，三星的 6 億像素 CMOS 尺寸會較大，可能不會搭載於手機上，而是針對汽車自動駕駛、物聯網等領域。"},{"pid":"5ea07907ef7bba356652957cd841ce0d01ccb485","tid":1982864,"uid":341649,"like":6,"dislike":29,"score":-23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:32:11.000Z","msg":"Sony已經唔玩手機像素遊戲<br />\n而家到Samsung玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 笑死"},{"pid":"e63a1e4d20467258bbf9f35bcc35f93bdeb9f183","tid":1982864,"uid":149959,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"5ea07907ef7bba356652957cd841ce0d01ccb485","tid":1982864,"uid":341649,"like":6,"dislike":29,"score":-23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:32:11.000Z","msg":"Sony已經唔玩手機像素遊戲<br />\n而家到Samsung玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 笑死"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:33:49.000Z","msg":"有冇睇最後嗰段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55868355f70862181234012666a1e3836fa6eee6","tid":1982864,"uid":33874,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"e63a1e4d20467258bbf9f35bcc35f93bdeb9f183","tid":1982864,"uid":149959,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"5ea07907ef7bba356652957cd841ce0d01ccb485","tid":1982864,"uid":341649,"like":6,"dislike":29,"score":-23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:32:11.000Z","msg":"Sony已經唔玩手機像素遊戲<br />\n而家到Samsung玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 笑死"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:33:49.000Z","msg":"有冇睇最後嗰段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:36:34.000Z","msg":"佢人生得手機，車都無架，你想佢點想像"},{"pid":"e712145440efefce98a1eeaeff6bde8b3ea9f459","tid":1982864,"uid":341649,"like":2,"dislike":14,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"55868355f70862181234012666a1e3836fa6eee6","tid":1982864,"uid":33874,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"e63a1e4d20467258bbf9f35bcc35f93bdeb9f183","tid":1982864,"uid":149959,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"5ea07907ef7bba356652957cd841ce0d01ccb485","tid":1982864,"uid":341649,"like":6,"dislike":29,"score":-23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:32:11.000Z","msg":"Sony已經唔玩手機像素遊戲<br />\n而家到Samsung玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 笑死"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:33:49.000Z","msg":"有冇睇最後嗰段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:36:34.000Z","msg":"佢人生得手機，車都無架，你想佢點想像"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T12:44:55.000Z","msg":"係呀窮撚住公屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要用Android <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗚嗚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c49ed05649803c